{"tid":686280,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有個善良知心嘅朋友 真係好過中六合彩","createTime":"2018-06-01T06:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T07:08:37.000Z","uid":162853,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6a97c03918e2d5c4a4acc2a314ab3fec5f10f3db","tid":686280,"uid":162853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"由細到大同屋企人關係都麻麻<br />\n老豆老母成日郁d就又打又鬧<br />\n好易發脾氣<br />\n搞到我個人都脾氣好差 同比較暴力<br />\n喺一年幾前工作關係識咗個朋友<br />\n佢份人好好 真誠 善良<br />\n好包容我嘅臭脾氣 又會不厭其煩開解我<br />\n成日勸我要收斂脾氣 同埋做多d導人向善嘅嘢<br />\n日子耐左實有回報<br />\n慢慢地喺佢影響下 發現自己脾氣真係比以前好<br />\n同屋企人關係都好咗<br />\n真係好多謝呢位朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朋友真係唔駛多 有一兩個好嘅就已經夠<br />\n足以改變一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d355823af4a6c1a94e7413b48258be05911430","tid":686280,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"異性?"},{"pid":"e43a276413bd72f7374198525019b2c32abc1ec0","tid":686280,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"以身相許啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcbae9fcdd022351b21b4bc333142bfa0a179d0","tid":686280,"uid":165482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de222cda72d40f07f3e2f385308ac4fdfa354a3b","tid":686280,"uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"我寧願中六合彩，少咁一個善良知心嘅朋友"},{"pid":"f2f1cc91aac6a3a03885cefd155d464a5191e0f7","tid":686280,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T0